data.description:
Welcome to this updated home nestled in the sought-after Walnut Hills community. A stunning fusion of modern design and comfort awaits you within these walls.
Explore the main level and be greeted by an expansive, open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living spaces. The heart of the home is the fully remodeled kitchen, adorned with sleek granite countertops, premium stainless steel appliances, a convenient double oven, and thoughtfully designed soft-close cabinets and drawers. Adding a touch of ambiance is the warm glow of under-cabinet lighting and custom pendant lights.
Enjoy the indoor-outdoor lifestyle as the kitchen flows effortlessly into a grand 266 square foot deck. Crafted from enduring, low-maintenance composite boards, this outdoor haven is destined for relaxation and entertainment.
The main level also features two inviting bedrooms, A completely remodeled 3/4 bath showcases contemporary finishes and fixtures, combining style and functionality.
Venture downstairs to the lower level, where garden-level windows bathe the space in natural sunlight. Discover a full bathroom, meticulously remodeled to mirror the home's elevated aesthetic. Additionally, two bedrooms grace this level—one boasting versatility as a non-conforming space, primed for a wardrobe closet or to become the perfect home office.
The lower level extends its generosity with a family room, setting the stage for cozy evenings and vibrant gatherings. A flexible bonus room beckons—an ideal canvas for a playroom, fitness or craft area catering to your unique needs.
Outside these walls, the neighborhood beckons with the charm of Cherry Creek's distinguished elementary schools, verdant parks, and winding trails. Enviably situated, this home boasts quick access to I-25, C-470, The Denver Tech Center, Park Meadows shopping district, and The Streets of Southglenn.
Bonus New: Windows-2023, carpeting-2023, interior paint-2023, roof-2022, AC unit-2020, water heater-2018,
